-On either, you have the option to create a variable inside a challange, but no way to set what for each team. I think we might need to get creative here on how we achieve this, maybe use a UX skill for this.
-Currently we dont support the assignments/random that we do on the web, this is fine for now, but we need to improve how we handle when a game that was setup on the web has multiple challanges for different teams. And we need this consistent across android and iOS.


